            Modern smartphones (iPhone 15 Pro, Samsung S24) produce excellent video 
            quality. Upgrade to a dedicated camera when you need: (1) Better autofocus 
            for moving subjects, (2) Interchangeable lenses for creative control, 
            (3) Superior low-light performance, or (4) Professional audio inputs.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you're just starting, use your phone and invest in lighting and audio first.
          </p>
        </div>
